name: HaruPage.getFillingColorSpace
purpose: Get the current filling color space

return.description:
Returns the current filling color space. The result value is one of the following:
   
    
     HaruDoc::CS_DEVICE_GRAY
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_DEVICE_RGB
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_DEVICE_CMYK
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_CAL_GRAY
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_CAL_RGB
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_LAB
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_ICC_BASED
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_SEPARATION
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_DEVICE_N
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_INDEXED
    
    
     HaruDoc::CS_PATTERN
